cp||at|^B@2^Y@3The no-trump echo is another interesting little gadget for signaling purposes. It is used to show the possession of only two cards of a suit when a long suit in the Dummy threatens to become established. It enables the hand holding the controlling cards to count the distribution of this particular suit with unerring accuracy, and frequently stops him from making an unnecessary hold-up. The no-trump echo may, like the trump echo, also be used negatively, which makes it an extremely valuable convention. The following deal shows the positive use of the no-trump echo: |
